Class JDBListData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBListData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class JDBListData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<JDBListData>
    JDBListData is a class which is used when displaying lists of data on screen via a JList with an optional graphical icon associated with each item. An example would be the list of users when some users have their accounts locked or disabled.
